transcript:

Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello. Hello. Sukhdev ji baat kar rahe hai, Chitra Digi showroom?
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Ji, sir Anurag baat kar raha tha India mart.com se aapne call kiya tha kal India mart par?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: India mart par?
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Chaliye main lagata hu main thoda sa abhi kahin baitha hu.
Customer: Achcha.
Executive: Main lagata hu thodi der mein. Services mein koi issue to nahi hai na sir? Matlab kuch concern tha ya aise hi matlab lag gaya tha call?
Customer: Haan services ke liye baat karna hai main lagata hu aapko thodi der mein.
Executive: Theek hai, theek hai. Ji.
